42:09.360 --> 42:12.000
Do you have children?
Yeah.

42:15.200 --> 42:17.400
No.

42:17.400 --> 42:20.960
No. I did have.

42:22.320 --> 42:24.000
I had a son.

42:28.120 --> 42:30.800
He found this world
a really tough place.

42:32.320 --> 42:34.600
And I wasn't there to...

42:38.640 --> 42:40.800
16...16 years old.

