44:11.080 --> 44:13.960
And I've decided
I don't want that anymore.

44:16.560 --> 44:20.120
Hey? Reach out, Jai.

44:21.320 --> 44:23.160
Talk to Barney.

44:26.160 --> 44:28.360
You are not alone in this.

44:29.760 --> 44:31.280
Truly.

44:36.560 --> 44:38.440
I better go.

44:41.760 --> 44:43.880
